{"id": 1222, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x雅培】最近你做过什么积极向上的尝试，让你的生活美好了一些？", "description": "人为制造的汹涌的小确幸。", "record_count": 6143, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160918144020b1npmRu76W4BGlSt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-19T03:00:36Z", "options": [{"id": 117761, "content": "每天十一点之前睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765138}, {"id": 117762, "content": "朋友帮我断舍离。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765146}, {"id": 117763, "content": "在网易云音乐上跟小秘书say  morning", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707545}, {"id": 123139, "content": "装作很活跃很善谈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792089}, {"id": 117765, "content": "\n近视500度以上，走路摘下眼镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752570}, {"id": 118021, "content": "开始学素描，虽然刚开始连线条都画不好；开始考bec中级，昨晚刚刚听了一节课，背了几个单词。突然发现原来空虚的晚上，也可以过得这么充足。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743273}, {"id": 127237, "content": "坚持六点起床", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681726}, {"id": 118023, "content": "热爱生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766508}, {"id": 134408, "content": "对于不喜欢的人第一时间表达老子很烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804638}, {"id": 117768, "content": "当然是跑步健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765214}, {"id": 117769, "content": "坚持每天跑步", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765218}, {"id": 119561, "content": "会把一些心里话同知心人说说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773552}, {"id": 119817, "content": "运动健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774544}, {"id": 117771, "content": "六点起床，喝一杯咖啡看一小时书，然后再洗漱吃饭上班。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523916}, {"id": 117772, "content": "少吃多餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590111}, {"id": 117773, "content": "写美食公众号，茜茜找吃的，非常有成就感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765252}, {"id": 119053, "content": "早睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770854}, {"id": 117774, "content": "跳舞一年多了，跳舞让人心情愉悦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702642}, {"id": 117776, "content": "坚持在睡前安静地看会书，或是戏剧或是诗集，伴着古典乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744694}, {"id": 117529, "content": "关闭朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 363, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527389}, {"id": 118809, "content": "一本接一本的书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770032}, {"id": 117530, "content": "用无硅油洗发水，貌似看到前额有一些头发新长出来了", "image": "img/option/option/20160919111139idj3Rf7k896hOeHF.jpg", "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701332}, {"id": 118554, "content": "啊啊啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 768936}, {"id": 118810, "content": "学着给自己做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770032}, {"id": 124442, "content": "自己和舍友一起做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681827}, {"id": 117531, "content": "锻炼了一年的胸，两天没练感觉像漏气一样憋了一点?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298191}, {"id": 118811, "content": "无聊的时间学习法语而不是发呆 胡思乱想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770032}, {"id": 117532, "content": "不理看着就心累的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 194, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433392}, {"id": 117533, "content": "每天上班路上，扛着相机，留住美好，即使只拍一张照片，也欣喜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708252}, {"id": 117534, "content": "强迫自己睡前不要玩手机，其实也没错过什么重要信息，像个夜猫子举着手机玩到半夜的日子也告一段落", "image": null, "praise_count": 165, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540126}, {"id": 117535, "content": "健身，每天感觉胸大了一点，背阔了一点（也许是错觉），但感觉真的很好，好像全世界只有自己在认真活似的，", "image": null, "praise_count": 238, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753619}, {"id": 117536, "content": "不怎麼瀏覽qdaily。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763911}, {"id": 117537, "content": "交了一个心地善良多才多艺的女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579720}, {"id": 117793, "content": "达到了自己给自己定的小目标。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765289}, {"id": 117538, "content": "十一点前睡，六点半前起", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668964}, {"id": 117539, "content": "早起去图书馆约自习", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182814}, {"id": 117540, "content": "只喝水", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182814}, {"id": 117541, "content": "开始背单词，开始用一些有用心去设计的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627213}, {"id": 117542, "content": "真的减了一点肥，是能让人看出来的一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 121382, "content": "关了手机震动和声音", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743774}, {"id": 117543, "content": "不随便买衣服了", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763925}, {"id": 118567, "content": "跳槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769190}, {"id": 117544, "content": "换个发型", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679826}, {"id": 118568, "content": "和家人一起出去玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692015}, {"id": 117545, "content": "《战争与和平》《肖申克的救赎》两本书看的连贯认真很多细节都能想起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669354}, {"id": 118057, "content": "今天上班的bus有座位坐--小确幸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761704}, {"id": 117546, "content": "买了个新耳机，让生活有更多音乐相伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684069}, {"id": 117547, "content": "吃中药，不长痘了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99741}, {"id": 117548, "content": "早起了，手游也不在沉迷了。整个人心情很轻松。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467335}, {"id": 117804, "content": "睡个好觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691633}]}